    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/f3f461f372efd9db6c21f65c99cd631d.poster.avif?t=1709120398\" width=620 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/f3f461f372efd9db6c21f65c99cd631d.webm?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/f3f461f372efd9db6c21f65c99cd631d.mp4?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏：</h2>一个VR玩家和一个屏幕玩家在同一台PC上的同一个虚拟世界中一起玩。VR玩家变成一个巨人，而屏幕玩家控制一个微小的人。只有通过共同努力，他们才能解决谜题并重获自由。<br><br>VR Giants通过利用两个完全不同输入设备的独特技术特性，以有趣和直观的方式激发快乐，教授善良和团队沟通。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/ca21ef4293a9defb997bf29def894a0e.poster.avif?t=1709120398\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/ca21ef4293a9defb997bf29def894a0e.webm?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/ca21ef4293a9defb997bf29def894a0e.mp4?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在你玩之前：</h2><i>该游戏旨在适应所有技能水平的玩家，让朋友、家人或重要的他人都能享受到乐趣。<br>您需要一个<strong>2m*2m的游戏区域</strong>。请确保您的游戏区域在开始VR Giants之前已经正确设置。<br><strong>警告：</strong> VR Giants需要VR玩家非常活跃地移动（下跪、上下移动等）。请只在您自己的责任范围内玩，并在感到疲劳时休息。</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >移动：</h2>在VR Giants中，移动方式与其他VR游戏有很大不同：不是巨人玩家可以在虚拟世界中选择自己的位置，而是微小玩家通过踩按钮激活新游戏区域来改变巨人的位置。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/318a56561f2c52b254b3f47ca18bd2ae.poster.avif?t=1709120398\" width=680 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/318a56561f2c52b254b3f47ca18bd2ae.webm?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/318a56561f2c52b254b3f47ca18bd2ae.mp4?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过沙漠、冰山、熔岩洞和牧场的冒险，享受精巧的谜题，拯救大卫的迷失的羊。学习如何利用歌利亚人不同的状态，例如：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>实体歌利亚人：巨人由一次按下并随后释放的按钮召唤。<br></li><li>临时歌利亚人：只要大卫持续按下按钮，歌利亚人就会出现在游戏区域。<br></li><li>火歌利亚人：巨人由岩浆制成，不能接触大卫或任何木质物品。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/617f81a8a9088274e832397ae018d7ba.poster.avif?t=1709120398\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/617f81a8a9088274e832397ae018d7ba.webm?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/617f81a8a9088274e832397ae018d7ba.mp4?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在不死的情况下进行冒险，得到众多奖励，如化妆品。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/d6e397b56820ffa54fd779b85604ec3b.poster.avif?t=1709120398\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1124160/extras/d6e397b56820ffa54fd779b85604ec3b.webm?t=1709120398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
